instructor.bio: Christine D’Ercole is a decorated track cyclist who brings this expertise to every Peloton class. Grounded in science, music, grit and grace, Christine believes that at all times you have two tools at your disposal: your breath and your inner monologue. In her class, you can expect Christine to empower Members to break through self-imposed limitations, and embrace their authentic selves and strength, both on and off the Bike.
instructor.short_bio: "I AM. I CAN. I WILL. I DO."
instructor.music_bio: Check out a sample of Christine’s current class playlist.
instructor.background: My classes are grounded in science, grit and grace. I will give you structured formats rooted in 20 years of competitive cycling experience set to playlists that push you farther than you thought possible.
ordered_q_and_as: Every class is an opportunity to put something across the finish line and make yourself proud. By showing up, turning it up and not giving up, we practice real-life skills that translate off the Bike.
BIKE RACING!, Wordshop™, writing, cooking, fine wine, scuba diving and photography.
instructor.quote: I AM. I CAN. I WILL. I DO.
instructor.name: Christine D'Ercole
